name: Dzyubak.GitHub.com
body:
![Dmytro Dzyubak](https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/7080467?v=3&s=460)

GitHub repositories store source code and code samples of my projects. Currently available repos:

* [JavaScript](https://github.com/dzyubak/javascript) - contains `SnowfallJS` project
* [C++](https://github.com/dzyubak/cpp) - contains `InformationSystem` / info-syst project (Console Application)
* [C#](https://github.com/dzyubak/cs) - contains Singly linked list written in C Sharp and an example of XML documentation generated by SharpDevelop with instructions on how to generate it. SinglyLinkedList XML documentation viewer is written specifically for this project. It formats XML file by using XSLT and HTML
* [Java](https://github.com/dzyubak/java) - contains `com.dzyubak.parser` program that searches for a number of double data type in a given String and performs like a parser or finite state machine (FSM)

More information about me can be found at [http://dzyubak.com/](http://dzyubak.com/)
